local Parallel = require "actions/Parallel" local Do = require "actions/Do" local Wait = require "actions/Wait"
return function(self, dt) if not self.scene:playerMovable() or self.stopMoving then return end
local fx = self.scene.player.fx if self.scene.player.noGas or self.nofollow then fx = 25 end
if self.bx < -1 then self.bx = self.bx + 1 elseif self.bx > 1 then self.bx = self.bx - 1 else self.bx = 0 end
local pbx = self.scene.player.bx if pbx > 0 then pbx = pbx + 1 end self.x = self.x + (fx + self.bx + pbx) * (dt/0.016) end
